--[[pod_format="raw",created="2026-02-15 17:25:45",modified="2026-05-13 02:38:16",revision=274]]
-- Picotron prototype: move + jump + aim/shoot + recoil + slide + shrine + dash(invuln + afterimage)
-- Player ammo uses single-shot guns that switch automatically after firing.
-- Gem score system with collection shards and off-screen indicator.
-- Melee combo prototype included.
-- English-only comments.

